<h4> Why Sydney Dev Camp? </h4>
<p>
I’m strongly motivated by a desire to learn and better
myself in everything I do.

</p><p>I tried learning online, through books and a lot of really
good resources. I found out that wasn’t the right approach for me. It was hard
to keep motivated.</p>

<p>Nothing is comparable to setting your life aside and moving
to another continent to immerse yourself in learning a new skill for 10 weeks.
It is amazing being with likeminded people who are trying to change their lives
and being part of a great community.</p>

<p>The most exciting thing is that I have the ability to change
the world, from my keyboard. This is how I came to be at Sydney Dev Camp.</p>
