<h4> Sydney. </h4>
<p>
I like to seek out and pursue experiences and I’m really
enjoying all the social and cultural aspects Sydney has to offer.
<p>I don’t always realize I’m in Sydney, since I spend all my
time coding. I’ve been exploring the city on the odd day, including a trip to
the Blue Mountains. I’ve been extremely fortunate in meeting amazing people and
sharing unforgettable adventures with them.</p>

<p>I don’t think I’ll ever get used to the fact that it rains
most days and the bizarre sounds of the birds. I’m currently investigating the
awful sound in the morning, I think it’s a crow.</p>
