<h4> My experiences so far. </h4>
<p>
I wake up and can’t wait to get to Sydney Dev Camp.

</p><p>I’m consistently being pushed to my limits, learning more
than ever before all while having more fun than I ever thought possible.</p>

<p>My experience overall has been great. I have learned more
than I thought was possible, I have made friends for life and have worked on
various interesting projects.</p>

<p><br></p>

<p><em>I want to do more, to be more
and to build more.</em></p>
